    "description": "Kirloskar Electric Advisory Limited has an exciting opening for a Quality Control Engineer at our Patna office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Kirloskar Electric Advisory Limited:\nKirloskar Electric Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare production cost analysis and efficiency reports\n• Implement 5S, Kaizen, and Six Sigma practices on the shop floor\n• Train and supervise shop floor workers and supervisors\n• Manage supplier quality audits and vendor development\n• Ensure compliance with safety regulations and factory acts\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n• Proficiency in TPM\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in APQP\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in Statistical Process Control\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Flexible working hours\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Patna, Bihar, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Kirloskar Electric Advisory Limited!",
